name: Princeton Premier
overview:
Princeton Premier is the fastest growing publisher of executive biographies in the world today.

With a membership comprised entirely of top tier professionals representing nearly every industry from around the globe, it is the most trusted third-party endorsement available today. Through long-standing relationships with the media, Fortune 500 companies, academic institutions and the Library of Congress, Princeton Premier offers unrivaled exposure for the purpose of networking, promoting, recruiting, partnering and increasing the position and worth of companies and individuals.

Princeton Premier is the most interactive online business community in the world. The company’s goal is to recognize excellence in every industry & profession and facilitate commerce & networking on all levels using the newest technology available. Their valued members use their web based services daily as an online channel to assist them in meeting their specific business goals. The versatility and ease of use of the Princeton Premier network makes connecting to the rest of the world cost effective and convenient.

Some basic features of the community include comprehensive member profiles, member search, live chat, instant messaging, discussion forums, member bulletins, private messaging, personal email accounts, investment news updates, member blogs, advertising space, classified listings, personal photo galleries and much more.
